22 holding certification from another state or within another
23 certification system in this state or another state;
24 [(7)] (6) "Coordinator", a staff person, hired by the
25 executive director of the Missouri commission for the deaf
26 and hard of hearing, who shall serve as coordinator for the
27 Missouri interpreter certification system;
28 [(8)] (7) "Deaf person", any person who is not able to
