1 209.299. The [board] commission shall schedule
2 evaluations for persons seeking certification, at a central
3 location, at least four times each year in 1995 and 1996,
4 and at least twice a year thereafter, according to the
5 number of applicants seeking certification. As soon as
6 possible after completion of an evaluation, the coordinator
