22 shall establish guidelines, and make recommendations to the
23 director of agriculture, for the use of funds appropriated
24 by the general assembly for the agriculture business
25 development division of the department of agriculture, and
26 for all funds collected or appropriated to the AgriMissouri
27 fund created pursuant to subsection 1 of this section. The
28 guidelines shall focus on the promotion of the AgriMissouri
